<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
  <title>Document</title>
  <style>
    *{
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
    }
    li{
      list-style: none;
    }
    .nav{
      width:100%;
      height:40px;
      background: #666666;
    }
    .nav-left{
      width:50%;
      height:40px;
      /* background: red; */
      float:left;
    }
    .nav-right{
      width:40%;
      height:40px;
      /* background: yellow; */
      float:right;
    }
    .nav-content li{
      float:left;
      font-size:11px;
      color:#CCCCCC;
      margin-left:45px;
      line-height:40px;
    }
    .nav-content li:hover{
      color: #fff;
      cursor: pointer;
    }
    .nav-content li:nth-child(1){
      margin-left:60px;
    }
    .nav-right li{
      float:right;
      font-size:11px;
      color:#CCCCCC;
      margin-left:10px;
      line-height:40px;
    }
    .nav-right li:hover{
      color: #fff;
      cursor: pointer;
    }
    .ver{
      margin-left:10px;
    }
    .login{
      margin-right:60px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="nav">
  <div class="nav-left">
    <ul class="nav-content">
      <li>TCL新闻</li>
      <li>企业采购</li>
      <li>经销商之家</li>
      <li>用户体验中心</li>
      <li>铁粉社区</li>
      <li>人才招聘</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class="nav-right">
    <li class="login"><%= nickName%></li>
    <li class="register">注册
      <span class="ver">|</span>
    </li>
    <li class="shopping">购物车
      <span class="ver">|</span>
    </li>
    <li class="weixin">微信商城
      <span class="ver">|</span>
    </li>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>